snippet.title: "Dinosaurs in Place — Dinosaur Puzzle Gameplay | Add to your Steam Wishlist!"
snippet.description:
"Love puzzles? Dinosaurs in Place is a new indie game that combines dinosaurs with logic challenges! In this video, we show 3 levels where you’ll see how to fit the dinosaur pieces onto the grid. Can you solve these puzzles? 🧩

Support the project by adding it to your Steam wishlist!

#WishlistNow #IndieDev #Dinosaurs #PuzzleGames #Gaming
